Kubernetes short names
ns - namesapces
po - pods
sa - serviceaccounts
svc - services
deploy - deployments
ing -ingress
netpol - networkpolicies
pv -persistentvolumes
pvc -persistentvolumeclaims
ev -events
quota - resourcequotas
ep - endpoints
cm - configmap


Delete multiple blank lines in vi
:g/^$/d
Delete a range of lines
:[start],[end]d. -> :3,5d
